mall>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayfocus_event\"><code>vrdisplayfocus</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypointerrestricted_event\"><code>vrdisplaypointerrestricted</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypointerunrestricted_event\"><code>vrdisplaypointerunrestricted</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypresentchange_event\"><code>vrdisplaypresentchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herança:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Resumo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Retorna um novo objeto <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> representando o resultado analisado da string&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Using_media_queries\" title=\"CSS/Media queries\">media query</a>&nbsp;especificada.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>mql</em> = window.matchMedia(<em>mediaQueryString</em>)</pre>\n\n<p>onde&nbsp;<code>mediaQueryString</code>&nbsp;é uma string representando a media query para o qual retorna um novo objeto&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchMedia</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"(min-width: 400px)\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>matches<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">/* a viewport tem pelo menos 400 pixels de largura */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">/* a viewport menos que 400 pixels de largura */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Este código permite-lhe lidar com as coisas de forma diferente quando a janela é muito estreita.</p>\n\n<p>Veja&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Testing_media_queries\" title=\"CSS/Using media queries from code\">Usando media queries a partir do código</a>&nbsp;para mais exemplos.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificações</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom-view/#dom-window-matchmedia\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Object Model (CSSOM) View Module<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'Window.matchMedia()' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Rascunho atual</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade do navegador","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>9</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/6\" title=\"Released on 2011-08-16.\">6.0</a> (6.0)</td>\n   <td>10</td>\n   <td>12.1</td>\n   <td>5.1</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>3.0</td>\n   <td>6.0 (6.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>12.1</td>\n   <td>5</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Using_media_queries\" title=\"CSS/Media queries\">Media queries</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Testing_media_queries\" title=\"CSS/Using media queries from code\">Usando media queries a partir do código</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryListListener</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Resumo","id":"summary"},{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"example"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Compatibilidade do navegador","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Retorna um novo objeto MediaQueryList (en-US) representando o resultado analisado da string media query especificada.","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Window.matchMedia()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Window.matchMedia()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"window.matchMedia","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"window.matchMedia","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Window.matchMedia()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Window.matchMedia()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Window.matchMedia()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/window/matchmedia","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/window/matchmedia/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window","title":"Window"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window/matchMedia","title":"Window.matchMedia()"}],"pageTitle":"Window.matchMedia() - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}